#. Tag: title
#: deployment_installserver.xml:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing an SMB Repository"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_installserver.xml:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using SMB, you can import the installation sources from a Microsoft Windows "
"server and start your Linux deployment even with no Linux machine around."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_installserver.xml:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set up an exported Windows Share holding your &productname; repository, "
"proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_installserver.xml:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Log in to your Windows machine."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_installserver.xml:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new directory that will hold the entire installation tree and name "
"it <filename>INSTALL</filename>, for example."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_installserver.xml:606
